Install libmeshpetscpackage
===========================

wajig install g77 mpich-bin libmpich1.0-dev refblas3-dev lapack3-dev
svn checkout http://libmeshpetscpackage.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ libmeshpetscpackage
cd libmeshpetscpackage/
./make

install grainmodel
==================

edit src/paths to point to your libmeshpetscpackage installation.

./make 

wajig install python-pexpect python-pyparsing python-syck gmsh
svn checkout http://femgeom.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ femgeom

usage
=====

input is the geometry in mesh/t.geo

./mesh
./assemble
./solve

output is the solution in tmp/sol.pos

to clean everything
===================

./clean

Documentation
=============

In the doc directory (see README there) to compile the tex sources.
